        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Ojo was well pleased.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "For a long time he had wished to explore the beautiful Land of Oz in which they lived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "At the foot of the mountain that separated the Country of the Munchkins from the Country of the Gillikins, the path divided.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "One way led to the left and the other to the right-straight up the mountain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Then they started on again and two hours later came in sight of the house of dr Pipt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Ah,\" said Ojo; \"you must be Dame Margolotte, the good wife of dr Pipt.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"We have come from a far lonelier place than this.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"A lonelier place!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "And in the Munchkin Country?\" she exclaimed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Then it must be somewhere in the Blue Forest.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"It is, good Dame Margolotte.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"And you must be Ojo the Unlucky,\" she added.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I never knew I was called the Unlucky,\" said Ojo, soberly; \"but it is really a good name for me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"How can I lose that 'Un,' Dame Margolotte?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I do not know how, but you must keep the matter in mind and perhaps the chance will come to you,\" she replied.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "There was a savory stew, smoking hot, a dish of blue peas, a bowl of sweet milk of a delicate blue tint and a blue pudding with blue plums in it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Do you wish to see dr Pipt on business or for pleasure?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"We are traveling,\" replied Ojo, \"and we stopped at your house just to rest and refresh ourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "The woman seemed thoughtful.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "The Magician is very busy, as I said, but if you will promise not to disturb him you may come into his workshop and watch him prepare a wonderful charm.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Thank you,\" replied the boy, much pleased.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I would like to do that.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Perhaps the Powder of Life couldn't either,\" said Ojo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Yes; it is perfection,\" she declared.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"A Glass Cat!\" exclaimed Ojo, astonished.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"What did old Mombi the Witch do with the Powder of Life your husband gave her?\" asked the boy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"She brought Jack Pumpkinhead to life, for one thing,\" was the reply. \"I suppose you've heard of Jack Pumpkinhead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"The more one knows, the luckier he is, for knowledge is the greatest gift in life.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"But tell me, please, what you intend to do with this new lot of the Powder of Life, which dr Pipt is making.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "He said his wife wanted it for some especial purpose.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I want it to bring my Patchwork Girl to life.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Oh!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "A Patchwork Girl?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "What is that?\" Ojo asked, for this seemed even more strange and unusual than a Glass Cat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I think I must show you my Patchwork Girl,\" said Margolotte, laughing at the boy's astonishment, \"for she is rather difficult to explain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"What is a patchwork quilt?\" asked Ojo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Is blue the only respectable color, then?\" inquired Ojo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Yes, for a Munchkin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "All our country is blue, you know.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000050_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000050_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "But in other parts of Oz the people favor different colors.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1180_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1180/1284_1180_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "I will show you what a good job I did,\" and she went to a tall cupboard and threw open the doors.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Chapter Three",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "The Patchwork Girl was taller than he, when she stood upright, and her body was plump and rounded because it had been so neatly stuffed with cotton.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Margolotte had first made the girl's form from the patchwork quilt and then she had dressed it with a patchwork skirt and an apron with pockets in it-using the same gay material throughout.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "All the fingers and thumbs of the girl's hands had been carefully formed and stuffed and stitched at the edges, with gold plates at the ends to serve as finger nails.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"She will have to work, when she comes to life,\" said Margolotte.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "The head of the Patchwork Girl was the most curious part of her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "If I get tired looking at her patched face I can whitewash it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Has she any brains?\" asked Ojo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"No; I am sure I am right about that,\" returned the woman.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"He means,\" explained Ojo, \"that unless your servant has good brains she won't know how to obey you properly, nor do the things you ask her to do.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Well, that may be true,\" agreed Margolotte; \"but, on the contrary, a servant with too much brains is sure to become independent and high and mighty and feel above her work.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "I want her to know just enough, but not too much.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Ingenuity,\" \"Amiability,\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Learning,\" \"Truth,\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Little,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"A little 'Cleverness'?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Quick, Margolotte!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Come and help me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "When the mixture was complete there was scarcely a handful, all told.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "No one saw him do this, for all were looking at the Powder of Life; but soon the woman remembered what she had been doing, and came back to the cupboard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "But the Magician replied:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"This powder must not be used before to morrow morning; but I think it is now cool enough to be bottled.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "Very carefully he placed the Powder of Life in the gold bottle and then locked it up in a drawer of his cabinet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I know; but that renders your uncle a most agreeable companion and gossip,\" declared dr Pipt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Most people talk too much, so it is a relief to find one who talks too little.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Don't you find it very annoying to be so crooked?\" he asked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"No; I am quite proud of my person,\" was the reply.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"I am not allowed to perform magic, except for my own amusement,\" he told his visitors, as he lighted a pipe with a crooked stem and began to smoke.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"Magic must be a very interesting study,\" said Ojo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"It truly is,\" asserted the Magician.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "\"What does the Liquid of Petrifaction do?\" inquired the boy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1284_1181_000040_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1284/1181/1284_1181_000040_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1284",
        "content": "It will never break nor wear out.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
